<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Key-Not-Found on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/key-not-found/</link><description>Recent content in Key-Not-Found on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/key-not-found/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::out_of_range - map.at() key not found</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-map/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-map/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="stdout_of_range---mapat-key-not-found"&gt;std::out_of_range - map.at() key not found&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::out_of_range&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when &lt;code&gt;map::at()&lt;/code&gt; is called with a key that does not exist in the map.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Key doesn&amp;#39;t exist
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; m &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {{&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;}};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; val &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; m.at(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws std::out_of_range
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Typo in key
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {{&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;localhost&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;}};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;config.at(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hosst&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// typo — throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Key set conditionally
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; m;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (condition) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; m[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;value&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;m.at(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws if condition was false
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-find-instead"&gt;Fix 1: Use find() instead&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; it &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; m.find(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (it &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; m.end()) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; val &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; it&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;second;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-count-first"&gt;Fix 2: Use count() first&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (m.count(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; val &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; m.at(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-operator-creates-default"&gt;Fix 3: Use operator[] (creates default)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; val &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; m[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// returns 0 if not found
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-vector/"&gt;std::out_of_range - vector.at()&lt;/a&gt; — vector index out of range.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-string/"&gt;std::out_of_range - string.at()&lt;/a&gt; — string index out of range.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-deque/"&gt;std::out_of_range - deque.at()&lt;/a&gt; — deque index out of range.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Ruby KeyError — Key Not Found in Hash Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/keyerror-ruby/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/keyerror-ruby/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;KeyError&lt;/code&gt; is raised when you access a hash using &lt;code&gt;fetch&lt;/code&gt; with a key that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist and no default value is provided. Unlike &lt;code&gt;[]&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;fetch&lt;/code&gt; raises an error instead of returning &lt;code&gt;nil&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using &lt;code&gt;fetch&lt;/code&gt; without a default for a missing key&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in hash key name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accessing nested hash with missing intermediate key&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data structure changed but code wasn&amp;rsquo;t updated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: fetch without default for missing key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;localhost&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;port &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; config&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# KeyError: key not found: &amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Provide a default value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;port &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; config&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3000&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 3000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Missing nested key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { name: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;address&lt;/span&gt;: { &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;city&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;NYC&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; } }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;zip &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:address&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:zip&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# KeyError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Use dig for safe nested access&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;zip &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;dig(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:address&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:zip&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Typo in key name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;settings &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;color&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;blue&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; settings&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;colour&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# KeyError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Verify key exists first&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; settings&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;key?(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;color&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) ? settings&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;color&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; : &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Simple fetch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:c&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# KeyError: key not found: :c&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:c&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Using a block&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;fetch(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:c&lt;/span&gt;) { &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;key&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; puts &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Missing key: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;#{&lt;/span&gt;key&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: Hash with default&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Hash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;new(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:missing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 0 (no error)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="nomethoderror-ruby"&gt;NoMethodError&lt;/a&gt; — calling method on nil from hash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="typeerror-ruby"&gt;TypeError&lt;/a&gt; — wrong type for hash operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="indexerror-ruby"&gt;IndexError&lt;/a&gt; — index out of range in array&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Swift Key Not Found — Dictionary Key Not Found Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/key-not-found-swift/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/key-not-found-swift/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="key-not-found--dictionary-key-not-found"&gt;Key Not Found — Dictionary Key Not Found&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A key not found error occurs when you access a dictionary key that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist without a default value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Swift dictionaries return optionals when accessing keys with subscript. However, if you force-unwrap the result of a missing key, or if your code expects a key to exist, you&amp;rsquo;ll get a runtime error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Missing key assumption&lt;/strong&gt; — assuming key exists without checking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Typo in key name&lt;/strong&gt; — misspelling dictionary key&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Config data&lt;/strong&gt; — missing configuration values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;API response&lt;/strong&gt; — unexpected keys in JSON data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Force unwrapping missing key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error: Unexpectedly found nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Typo in key name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; config: [String: String] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;userName&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; name = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;username&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// nil (case sensitive)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Missing nested key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; data: [String: [String: Int]] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;scores&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;math&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;95&lt;/span&gt;]]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; science = data[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;grades&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;science&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Wrong key type&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// nil (Int vs String key)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-optional-binding"&gt;Fix 1: Use optional binding&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(value)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Key not found&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-nil-coalescing"&gt;Fix 2: Use nil coalescing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] ?? &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-default-values"&gt;Fix 3: Use default values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-safe-subscript"&gt;Fix 4: Use safe subscript&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; data: [String: [String: Int]] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;scores&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;math&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;95&lt;/span&gt;]]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; science = data[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;grades&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;science&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; science = data[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;grades&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]?[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;science&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// nil, no crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe dictionary access&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; config: [String: Any] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;theme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;dark&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fontSize&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; theme = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;theme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? String ?? &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;light&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; fontSize = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fontSize&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Int ?? &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Dictionary with defaults&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; wordCount: [String: Int] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;wordCount[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;wordCount[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// [&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;: 6, &amp;#34;world&amp;#34;: 1]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/nil-unwrap/"&gt;Nil Unwrap&lt;/a&gt; — force unwrapping nil&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/force-unwrap/"&gt;Force Unwrap&lt;/a&gt; — bang operator crash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/array-index/"&gt;Array Index Out of Range&lt;/a&gt; — index beyond bounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Registry Key Not Found Error - How to Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/windows/reg-key-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/windows/reg-key-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="registry-key-not-found-error"&gt;Registry Key Not Found Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when a program or script tries to read or write a registry key that does not exist. The error typically reads:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;The system cannot find the path specified.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Cannot find key [path].&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is common in scripts, installers, and system utilities that reference registry paths that were deleted, never created, or are typed incorrectly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Typo in the registry path&lt;/strong&gt; — The key path is misspelled or uses incorrect separators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key was deleted&lt;/strong&gt; — Previous cleanup or uninstall removed the key.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Application not installed&lt;/strong&gt; — The software that creates the key is not installed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrong registry hive&lt;/strong&gt; — Looking in &lt;code&gt;HKLM&lt;/code&gt; when the key is in &lt;code&gt;HKCU&lt;/code&gt;, or vice versa.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;32-bit vs 64-bit registry&lt;/strong&gt; — 32-bit keys are under &lt;code&gt;Wow6432Node&lt;/code&gt; on 64-bit systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="verify-the-key-exists"&gt;Verify the Key Exists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check if the registry key exists before accessing it:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>